children.description:
**`test/uninstall.test.ts`** is a unit test suite for `gstack-uninstall`, which removes Garry Tan's gstack agent skills from the user's environment while preserving optional settings and non-gstack tools.

- All syntax passes, including flag parsing for optional removal settings;
- Roots for distributed skills and application state preserve integrity during uninstallation;
- Destructive flag `--force` completely clears skills and state directories, explicitly bypassing the `/gstack-upgrade` process;
- Clean system outputs informative messages without erroring on missing or invalid installations;
- Prefixed installations (post-setup `--no-prefix`) are fully reversed by the uninstall binary, syncing both old and new skill paths simultaneously;
